title: Cilcain shed fire death inquiry continues
text: An investigation is continuing after a body was discovered by firefighters following a shed blaze in Flintshire. North Wales Fire and Rescue Service was called to Cilcain, near Mold, just after 16:00 BST on Tuesday. Firefighters are due to return to the scene on Wednesday. North Wales Police is investigating the incident. Share this story About sharing
